## âš™ï¸ Kafka & Docker Setup

Kafka is configured as a **3-broker cluster** with Zookeeper. Kafka UI is also included for easier topic/message inspection.

### Dockerized Services:

- ğŸ§  Zookeeper
- ğŸ“¦ Kafka brokers (kafka1, kafka2, kafka3)
- ğŸ›ï¸ Online shopping app (Producer)
- ğŸ“¥ Kafka consumer service
- ğŸ–¥ï¸ Kafka UI (on port 8080)

